"Cerceris quadricincta: iso. Richards: 1980","212","NT","Adrian Knowles","Moderation","I'd have preferred VU! I've not seen it around Colchester in recent years (has Mike found it at Middlewick?!).  Many of the Kent sites are probably very vulnerable to development or loss of habitat to coastal processes, succession etc.  This should definitely be ""of concern"".","1","N"
