"Ancistrocerus antilope","212","CR","Steven Falk","","Probably our rarest mason wasp. Catastrophic national decline historically (from literature but not captured by BWARS). Only one modern record (David Notton about 4-5 years ago) but seemingly not in BWARS dataset. Prior to that I think the last record for it (and its special Chrysis pseudobrevitarsis cuckoo) was mine from N. Devon in 1989. Species needs inclusion if possible.","0",""
