"Ancistrocerus parietinus: iso. Richards: 1980","212","NT?","Steven Falk","","No data sheet provided. Very clear indication of a serious UK decline in the map (much more obvious than species like Bombus bohemicus or B. campestris). I rarely see it now.","1","Undergraded?"
