"Hylaeus dilatatus: iso. Notton and Dathe: 2008","212","","Steven Falk","","You've treated it as LC rather than DD (which I approve of) but it shows inconsistency with the way you have handled other species like Andrena ovatula, A. pilipes, Nomada panzeri etc.","0","Y"
