"Andrena ampla: iso. Falk et al: 2019","212","LC?","Liam Olds","","Is there enough information in Falk et. al. 2019 to asign a Status? Based on examined specimens in that paper, ampla appears to be widespread in the south-west (including Wales). Suspect its LC. ","1","N"
